        "subject": "LU-6932 utils: bound check the index in llog_reader",
        "message": "LU-6932 utils: bound check the index in llog_reader\n\nA corrupted file can crash the llog_reader utility, if the index read\nis out of bound. Add an extra check to catch that case.\n\nAlso fixed a typo, and replaced a printf with llapi_error, since\nerrors should go to stderr, and updated its error message with better\ninformation.\n\nSigned-off-by: frank zago <fzago@cray.com>\nChange-Id: I16abe55081cccc8363f6b31c57710ea154e9037e\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/master"
    }
